<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>

<meta charset="UTF-8" />
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />

<title>News | PanorOmics</title>

<style>

body{
  margin:0;
  background:#020817;
  color:white;
  font-family:Inter,sans-serif;
  line-height:1.7;
}

.news-wrapper{
  max-width:1100px;
  margin:0 auto;
  padding:64px 24px 48px;
}

.news-kicker{
  color:#3b82f6;
  font-size:.72rem;
  letter-spacing:.24em;
  font-weight:700;
  margin-bottom:18px;
}

.news-title{
  font-size:2.6rem;
  line-height:1;
  letter-spacing:-0.05em;
  margin-bottom:18px;
}

.news-title span{
  color:#3b82f6;
}

.news-intro{
  color:#cbd5e1;
  max-width:760px;
  font-size:.95rem;
  margin-bottom:42px;
}

.news-card{
  background:#07111f;
  border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.08);
  border-radius:22px;
  padding:34px;
  box-shadow:0 20px 60px rgba(0,0,0,.22);
}

.news-meta{
  color:#60a5fa;
  font-size:.75rem;
  font-weight:700;
  letter-spacing:.16em;
  margin-bottom:14px;
}

.news-card h2{
  font-size:1.65rem;
  line-height:1.2;
  margin-bottom:16px;
}

.news-card p{
  color:#cbd5e1;
  font-size:.94rem;
  max-width:840px;
  margin-bottom:24px;
}

.news-actions{
  display:flex;
  gap:14px;
  flex-wrap:wrap;
}

.news-button{
  display:inline-flex;
  align-items:center;
  justify-content:center;
  padding:13px 22px;
  border-radius:999px;
  background:#2563eb;
  color:white;
  text-decoration:none;
  font-size:.9rem;
  font-weight:700;
  transition:.25s ease;
}

.news-button:hover{
  transform:translateY(-2px);
  box-shadow:0 12px 34px rgba(37,99,235,.28);
}

.news-button.secondary{
  background:transparent;
  border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.18);
  color:#dbe4ee;
}

.news-footer{
  margin-top:48px;
  padding-top:20px;
  border-top:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.06);
  color:#64748b;
  font-size:.8rem;
  text-align:center;
}

@media(max-width:768px){

  .news-wrapper{
    padding:48px 18px 34px;
  }

  .news-title{
    font-size:2.1rem;
  }

  .news-card{
    padding:24px;
  }

}

</style>

</head>

<body>

<main class="news-wrapper">

  <div class="news-kicker">
    NEWS & ANNOUNCEMENTS
  </div>

  <h1 class="news-title">
    PanorOmics <span>News</span>
  </h1>

  <p class="news-intro">
    Institutional updates, educational announcements,
    research communications, and public-facing releases
    from the PanorOmics Omics Sciences Center.
  </p>

  <article class="news-card">

    <div class="news-meta">
      ANNOUNCEMENT • 2026
    </div>

    <h2>
      PanorOmics Announces Upcoming Free Omics Sciences 101 Educational Series
    </h2>

    <p>
      PanorOmics will launch a free introductory Omics Sciences 101 Series
      covering six major omics disciplines: genomics, transcriptomics,
      proteomics, metabolomics, lipidomics, and epigenomics. The initiative
      is designed to introduce contemporary omics sciences and prepare
      learners, researchers, and future scientists for deeper engagement
      in systems biology, computational biology, AI biology, and
      translational biotechnology.
    </p>

    <div class="news-actions">

      <a
        href="/PanorOmics_News_Announcement.pdf"
        target="_blank"
        class="news-button"
      >
        Read Announcement PDF
      </a>

      <a
        href="/education"
        class="news-button secondary"
      >
        Explore Education
      </a>

    </div>

  </article>

  <div class="news-footer">
    PanorOmics © 2026 • Pittsburgh, PA • USA
  </div>

</main>

</body>

</html>
